Title: Creating Customer Segments
Slug: creating-customer-segments
Date: 2017-01-05 12:00
Category: Machine Learning
Tags: python, Clustering, Pca/ica, Sklearn, Feature selection, Visualizing data
Author: German Rezzonico
Summary: Performed Exploratory Data Analysis. Analyzed feature relevance. Performed feature selection. Preprocessed data: feature scaling, outlier detection. Implemented Feature Transformation: PCA/ICA. Applied unsupervised learning algorithm: clustering. Reviewed unstructured data to understand the patterns and natural categories that the data fits into. Used multiple algorithms and both empirically and theoretically compared and contrasted their results. Made predictions about the natural categories of multiple types in a dataset, then checked these predictions against the result of unsupervised analysis.
